## Appendix B: Story Development Questions

### Prioritization Questions
| Question                                             | BRD Section Reference | Purpose              | Expected Output           |
| ---------------------------------------------------- | --------------------- | -------------------- | ------------------------- |
| Which stories deliver the highest business value?    | User Stories          | Value prioritization | Ranked story backlog      |
| What are the technical dependencies between stories? | Dependencies          | Sprint planning      | Dependency-aware roadmap  |
| Which stories are needed for minimum viable product? | Epic Overview         | MVP definition       | Core story identification |

### Epic Questions
| Question                                                  | BRD Section Reference    | Purpose              | Expected Output             |
| --------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------ | -------------------- | --------------------------- |
| Does this epic align with user personas and journey maps? | Epic Description         | User validation      | Persona-validated epic      |
| What are the measurable business outcomes expected?       | Epic Acceptance Criteria | Success metrics      | Measurable success criteria |
| How does this epic integrate with existing systems?       | Technical Notes          | Integration planning | Integration requirements    |

### Estimation Questions
| Question                                            | BRD Section Reference | Purpose           | Expected Output             |
| --------------------------------------------------- | --------------------- | ----------------- | --------------------------- |
| Are the acceptance criteria clear and testable?     | Acceptance Criteria   | Quality assurance | Refined acceptance criteria |
| What are the technical risks for each story?        | Technical Notes       | Risk assessment   | Risk-adjusted estimates     |
| Do we have all the information needed to implement? | Story Details         | Readiness check   | Definition of ready         |

### Sprint Questions
| Question                                                | BRD Section Reference | Purpose           | Expected Output             |
| ------------------------------------------------------- | --------------------- | ----------------- | --------------------------- |
| Can the team commit to the proposed sprint scope?       | Sprint Planning       | Capacity planning | Realistic sprint commitment |
| Are there any blockers or dependencies for this sprint? | Dependencies          | Sprint execution  | Dependency resolution plan  |
| What is the sprint goal and how do stories support it?  | Sprint Planning       | Sprint alignment  | Clear sprint objective      |

### Testing Questions
| Question                                                 | BRD Section Reference | Purpose           | Expected Output         |
| -------------------------------------------------------- | --------------------- | ----------------- | ----------------------- |
| Are all acceptance criteria testable and measurable?     | Acceptance Criteria   | Test planning     | Testable criteria       |
| What are the performance and security test requirements? | Testing Strategy      | Quality assurance | Comprehensive test plan |
| How will user acceptance testing be conducted?           | Testing Approach      | UAT planning      | UAT execution plan      |

